- **Description:**

Migrated the Řehoř dashboard UI from custom HTML/CSS components to PatternFly 6.

### Changes Made

**Layout & Navigation**
- Replaced custom header with PF Masthead + Toolbar
- Converted tab navigation to PF Nav (horizontal variant)
- Converted InstanceSelector from plain select to PF Select

**Theme Support**
- Added full theme switcher dropdown (Theme: Default/Project Felt, Color Scheme: System/Light/Dark, Contrast Mode: System/Default/High Contrast/Glass)
- Theme state persisted in localStorage
- Custom CSS variables mapped to PF design tokens for automatic theme adaptation
- Glass mode support with isGlass prop on Cards

**Components Converted**
- Instances page — PF Card with CardHeader/CardBody/CardFooter, Icon, Label, LabelGroup, Divider
- TaskCard — PF Card with status-colored left border, Label for status/repo/artifacts
- MemoryCard — PF Card with LabelGroup for category/tags
- BotBanner — PF Card with Flex layout, Label, Icon, Button
- DetailPanel (Task & Memory) — PF Card, DescriptionList, CodeBlock, Button, Label
- CycleRunCard — PF Card with Label for type/metrics
- CycleRunDetail — PF Card, DescriptionList, Divider, SearchInput, ToggleGroup
- TaskGroupCard — PF Card with download Button, Label, LabelGroup
- Pagination — PF Pagination component
- Toasts — PF AlertGroup with Alert (isToast, auto-timeout)
- Search page — PF SearchInput
- Memories page — PF Select dropdowns for filters
- Tasks page — PF Select for status filter
- Costs page — PF Card wrappers, ToggleGroup for metrics/date mode, Select for days

**Icons**
- Replaced custom text/emoji icons with PF icons (TimesIcon, ExpandIcon, CompressIcon, DownloadIcon, CircleIcon, SunIcon, MoonIcon, AdjustIcon, ExclamationTriangleIcon)

**Mock Data**
- Added 4 archived tasks to mock-server for testing the Archive page
